{"tid":1453694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（朋友叫代post）黑警扮義載 呃細路上車截查！","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T22:56:23.000Z","uid":52740,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a9967d9308a0d9d9b79f8dc90aa767f5ddb81121","tid":1453694,"uid":52740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:03:10.000Z","msg":"好攰，但一定要寫呢件事出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n琴晚義載，三位護救義工需要由葵芳去黃埔，其中一位話前晚誤上狗車，黑警扮義載，但係唔係車佢去目的地，反而喺車上不斷問佢去過邊、做過乜，然後就車佢去附近road block<br />\n<br />\n呢位義工機警，發現唔係去緊目的地，仲見到下一條街有road block, 佢即刻開車門跳車走，跟住個司機同副駕馬上落車追，好彩最後義工走得甩，否則後果會點，大家一定想像到。<br />\n<br />\n依家黑警冇野做唔出，唔止扮示威者，仲會扮義載，呃啲細路上車然後套佢地講野，甚至車佢地去截查。<br />\n<br />\n義載係市民對示威者嘅支持同心意，班黑警咁做真係喪心病狂！希望大家保持警覺，唔好畀黑警有機可乘！"},{"pid":"6df9c3aeafd80bd00224aaf6062c4a663e8bcf3a","tid":1453694,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttLEooS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttLEooS.png&h=4b443cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxZmxjw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxZmxjw.png&h=1d33d451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g1fEi4i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg1fEi4i.png&h=ea27d434&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81ee0330bdfc60b7ccc7a18b469a10802b231f01","tid":1453694,"uid":258210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:04:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5830e886f8f79a286f1ca6d633e3db7d81d12ed","tid":1453694,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47bb2966cde554394e3dc9bca99032a718475185","tid":1453694,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"